<view class="page settings-page notification-settings-page">
  <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="settings-hint">加载中…</view>
  <block wx:else>
    <view class="form-hint-block">
      开启后，在创建提醒时可选择微信通知（仍需在微信弹窗中授权）。编辑已有提醒不会重新弹出订阅。
    </view>
    <view class="inset-group">
      <view class="settings-cell">
        <view class="settings-cell-main">
          <text class="settings-label">微信通知总开关</text>
          <text class="cell-meta">关闭后创建提醒时不再提供微信提醒选项</text>
        </view>
        <switch
          checked="{{wechatEnabled}}"
          disabled="{{saving}}"
          bindchange="onWechatEnabledChange"
          color="{{switchColor}}"
        />
      </view>
      <view class="settings-cell">
        <view class="settings-cell-main">
          <text class="settings-label">新建提醒默认开启通知</text>
          <text class="cell-meta">仅当总开关开启且服务端已配置模板时生效</text>
        </view>
        <switch
          checked="{{defaultReminderEnabled}}"
          disabled="{{saving || !wechatEnabled}}"
          bindchange="onDefaultReminderChange"
          color="{{switchColor}}"
        />
      </view>
      <view wx:if="{{quietHoursText}}" class="settings-cell stack">
        <view class="settings-cell-main">
          <text class="settings-label">免打扰时段</text>
          <text class="cell-meta">{{quietHoursText}}（由服务端配置，暂不可在小程序修改）</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view wx:if="{{!templateConfigured}}" class="settings-cell stack">
        <view class="settings-cell-main">
          <text class="settings-label">模板状态</text>
          <text class="cell-meta">服务端尚未配置微信提醒模板，开关保存后仍无法推送。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
